<figureCitation box="[836,904,1999,2025]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="32.[188,231,1927,1953]" captionTargetBox="[189,1340,495,1901]" captionTargetId="figure@32.[189,1399,476,1902]" captionTargetPageId="32" captionText="Fig. 8. Sphegina (Asiosphegina) amplistylus sp. nov., holotype, Ƌ. A. Sternum IV, ventral view. B. Left surstylus, lateral view. C. Left superior lobe, lateral view. D. Genitalia, right side, lateral view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3830555" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3830555/files/figure.png" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
